body_html:
Hey @phizaz great to hear that AutoGraph is useful to you. If you are able, we'd love if you could share the code that you used it in!
We're still actively working on AutoGraph, so to get the most out of it (before TF 2.0 is released), staying on nightly gets you the most bug-fixes and functionality.
However, if that's not possible, try using the 1.10 release or later.
